<template>
  <VueMultiselect :options="users"/>
</template>

<script>
import VueMultiselect from 'vue-multiselect'
import axios from "axios";
export default {
  name: "AdminRemoveLessons",
  components : {
    VueMultiselect
  },
  data(){
    return{
      users : null
    }
  },
  methods : {
    async fetchUsers(){
      try {
        const response = await axios.get('ServletAdminGetBookings',{params : {action : 'getListOfUsers',device : 'web'}});
        this.users = response.data;
        console.log(response.data);
      }catch (e){
        console.error(e.response);
        if(e.response.status === 401){
          this.$handle_session_expired()
        }
      }
    },

    async fetchBookingsForUser(){
      try {
        const response = await axios.get('ServletAdminGetBookings',{params : {action : 'getBookingsForUser',device : 'web',userEmail : 'giacomodamosso@gmail.com'}});
        console.log(response.data);
      }catch (e){
        console.error(e.response);
        if(e.response.status === 401){
          this.$handle_session_expired()
        }
      }
    }
  },
  computed : {
    userData(){
      return this.users;
    }
  }
}
</script>

</style>
